text.section:
The following individuals are exempt from this subtitle:
A registered mortgage loan originator, when acting for an entity described in § 11-601(w) of this subtitle;
An individual who offers or negotiates the terms of a mortgage loan with or on behalf of an immediate family member of the individual;
An individual who offers or negotiates the terms of a mortgage loan secured by a dwelling that served as the individual's residence;
A licensed attorney who negotiates the terms of a mortgage loan on behalf of a client as an ancillary matter to the attorney's representation of the client, unless the attorney is compensated by a mortgage lender, a mortgage broker, or a mortgage loan originator, or by an agent of a mortgage lender, mortgage broker, or mortgage loan originator; and
Subject to subsection (e) of this section, an individual loan servicer.
